title: 08/16/21 DPS Hour 1 Matt Hayes
itunes:title: 08/16/21 DPS Hour 1 Matt Hayes
description:
Doug Gottlieb and Rob Parker, in for Dan, react from the first looks at the rookie quarterback class from this weekend's preseason action. Matt Hayes from 1010 XL Jacksonville joins the guys to discuss Tim Tebow's effort to break the Jaguars' roster and explain why there is huge optimism for the Urban Meyer regime in Jacksonville. Plus, the guys debate who is the best player in baseball, Fernando Tatis Jr. or Shohei Ohtani?
